title: Deus Ex: Human Revolution. Official Game Trailer [Episode 159 SD
description:
Release Date: 8/23/2011
Platforms: PC, PS3, Xbox360
Developer: Eidos Interactive
Genres: First-Person, Role-Playing, Shooter
ESRB: M (Blood; Drug Reference; Intense Violence; Sexual Themes; Strong Language; Use of Alcohol)


Synopsis:

You play Adam Jensen, a security specialist, hand-picked to oversee the defense of one of America's most experimental biotechnology firms. But when a black ops team breaks in and kills the scientists you were hired to protect, everything you thought you knew about your job changes.

Is Brink really a bad game? Plus, more Dark Souls talk, the debut of Starhawk and spend some serious time with Deus Ex: Human Revolution!
